    "body": "### Problem\n\n![Image](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/b12ffb57-18e7-4bd9-952a-18ba180fe668)\n\nbuffer contents:\n```\nThis is a test\nЭто тест\n\n```\n\nThe line 2 has a gap of 1 space after each Cyrillic character. Line 1 provided as reference. Using font Iosevka Nerd Font (nerd-fonts 3.4.0), but reproducible with any font, not just Iosevka or nerd fonts.\nThis is also not caused by the terminal itself, as other programs output cyrillic characters as expected:\n\n![Image](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/fdfe0ea1-d4ee-49be-b620-447b9806a864)\n\n### Steps to reproduce\n\nopen nvim\ntype cyrillic characters\n\n### Expected behavior\n\ncyrillic characters have the normal width:\n\n![Image](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/fdfe0ea1-d4ee-49be-b620-447b9806a864)\n\n### Nvim version (nvim -v)\n\n0.11.0\n\n### Vim (not Nvim) behaves the same?\n\nno, vim 9.1.0794\n\n### Operating system/version\n\nGentoo Linux\n\n### Terminal name/version\n\nGnome Terminal 3.52.2 for GNOME 46\n\n### $TERM environment variable\n\nxterm-256color\n\n### Installation\n\nGentoo official repository ebuild",
