        {
            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "Found the cause and solution - Installing from ebuild 0.11.0-r2 (which is currently marked as unstable) solves the issue.\n\nThe solution seems to have been added already in r1: https://gitweb.gentoo.org/repo/gentoo.git/commit/?id=782858d054b00b6bfa1d42e46790afc1fb497326\n\nIt's because of gentoo's libutf8proc, the r2 ebuild disables the `cjk` USE flag and the cyrillic characters display properly now",
            "created_at": "2025-05-21T12:54:46Z",
            "html_url": "https://github.com/neovim/neovim/issues/34114#issuecomment-2897867629",
